The love you deserve is out there… trust me…

Thank you for coming to my Ted talk  💸

One day someone will walk into your life and be everything you could ever hope and wish for and you’re gonna love them very much and this time they’ll love you back. So don’t waste your time being dealing with someone who puts you to the side.

When someone cares about you you’ll see them move mountains, swim across oceans, leap off of the highest places just to experience who you are as a person. You are a prime example of that in the way you care for said person.

They’re free to do whatever they please with you. This isn’t always a bad thing because when you care about someone it’s human to do things that makes them happy. But you must remember if they truly appreciate you,they wouldn’t make you ask yourself if they did.

your comfort in how you’re feeling prevents you from actually progressing sure it’s sweet and it’s nice but if you wait in line for your turn which,might I add,may never happen. You put yourself in the other persons disposal. Meaning…

Perhaps loving someone who doesn’t give you the same thing back is in a weird way something you’re comfortable with because you’re use to the idea of hoping that one day they’ll love you back and the hope that you get from that is exhilarating however…
